description:
The Hills of Hate!

It seemed only yesterday tha I was with the boys on the block, charging up a hill, trying to knock the Bleeker St. gang off it but not it was today! And I was advancing up another hill with the boys -- trying to knock another gang off it!

Combat Diver!

He was the allies last hope -- trapped beneath the surface of the North Sea with the war's most prized cargo! But how can a man hope to survive under thirty five fathoms of wate without an air line and also defeat a ruthless enemy?

Untitled

This story has no title! Once you start reading we feel you will agree with us! If you don't -- you can find a name for it yourself -- on the last page!

The Navy's Frogmen (Text only story)

Battlefield Touchdown!

It takes a big man to be a football tackle, big in more ways that one. But what happens when the cheering crowds are gone and the opposing tackle is -- Death?
name: The Hills of Hate!; Combat Diver!; Untitled; The Navy's Frogmen; Battlefield Touchdown!

description:
One Second to Zero

It was Jim Nelson's job to plant traps -- not to step into them! But he couldn't tell what the fortunes of war had in store for him! Or how he would act when caught in the most startling of traps -- with the knowledge he had to escape before... One Second to Zero

Mosquito Boat!

A New PT Boat Captain must be more than just the top officer on his tiny command, he must become the brains and heart of his crew! But when his own men spurn his friendship, and mistrust his ability -- the fighting cract can become a floating death trap!

Playoff On Slaughter Hill!

It was Sgt. Ricky Olsen's last chance to manage a pennant winning ball club! But the odds were all against him! His opponents had limitless reserves and boasted fat shelling averages! And there were no umpires to enforce the rules, or loyal fans to cheer him on in... Playoff On Slaughter Hill!

The Flying Cameras (Text only story)

Beginner's Luck!

Five tanks rumbled toward the shell-torn town of Wahung! Veteran Sgt. Sawyer, in the lead tank, knew how battle savvy paid off! But he groaned whenever he looked at his crew! They were all green recruits! What chance would they have in the combat that loomed ahead?
name: One Second to Zero; Mosquito Boat!; Playoff On Slaughter Hill!; The Flying Cameras; Beginner's Luck!
